comments: Bridges (PHX) brings his hand toward VanVleet's (TOR) path and marginal contact occurs with VanVleet's front during the drive.
Bridges (PHX) and Paul (PHX) legally contest VanVleet's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Barnes (TOR) and Bridges (PHX) engage and disengage with one another off-ball.
VanVleet (TOR) and Paul (PHX) briefly engage and disengage off ball.
Paul (PHX) establishes himself in Barnes' (TOR) path and does not deliver illegal contact.
VanVleet (TOR) brings his right arm to the side and marginal contact occurs with Craig's (PHX) front as Craig retrieves the rebound.
Ayton (PHX) and Barnes (TOR) briefly engage and disengage during rebounding, and marginal contact occurs as Craig (PHX) secures the rebound.
Craig (PHX) and Siakam (TOR) engage and disengage with one another as they move toward the wing off-ball.
VanVleet (TOR) and Bridges (PHX) briefly engage and disengage as they cut across the lane.
Siakam (TOR) is already in Johnson's (PHX) path and absorbs the marginal body contact that occurs as they come together in transition.
Paul (PHX) brings his off arm towards Trent Jr.'s (TOR) front and marginal contact occurs as Paul releases from the contact.
Trent Jr. (TOR) brings his right arm forward and makes clean contact with the ball as he defends Paul (PHX) near half-court.
Barnes (TOR) and Craig (PHX) each raise an arm as they pursue the rebound and incidental contact occurs as Craig retrieves the ball and simultaneously attempts the controlled tip.
Barnes (TOR) brushes Ayton's (PHX) right arm and marginal contact occurs during Ayton's put-back attempt.
Johnson (PHX) cleanly deflects the ball away from VanVleet (TOR) on the perimeter.
Possession is awarded to TOR. However, VanVleet (TOR) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.  Possession should have been awarded to PHX.
Barnes (TOR) and Johnson (PHX) come together at the same spot as incidental contact occurs during rebounding.
Siakam (TOR) engages and disengages with Lee (PHX) during the inbound.
VanVleet (TOR) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
Siakam (TOR) commits a take foul on Lee (PHX).
Paul (PHX) legally contests Trent Jr.'s (TOR) jump shot attempt and would avoid Trent Jr. if he did not slightly extend his right leg forward to initiate the marginal contact.
Barnes (TOR) and Johnson (PHX) engage and disenage with one another after the release of the jump shot attempt.
Johnson (PHX) is the last player to touch the ball before it goes out of bounds.
VanVleet (TOR) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
Trent Jr. (TOR) gives a step of distance when establishing himself in Bridges' (PHX) path and he absorbs the contact.
Paul (PHX) brushes Siakam's (TOR) arm, causing SIakam to momentarily lose possession before he immediately recovers the loose ball.
Siakam (TOR) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before elevating for the layup attempt.
Siakam (TOR) does not intentionally knock the ball away from Lee (PHX) as Lee moves to inbound.
Lee (PHX) releases the inbound pass prior to his right foot landing in-bounds.
VanVleet (TOR) commits a take foul on Johnson (PHX).
Johnson (PHX) legally contests Trent Jr.'s (TOR) jump shot attempt.
Achiuwa (TOR) commits a take foul on Paul (PHX).
Siakam (TOR) gathers the ball on his right foot and takes two steps before entering his upward shooting motion.
Bridges (PHX) legally contests Siakam's (TOR) jump shot attempt.
